    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "My name is Simeon Agbanoma and I am a resident at Beavers Estate situated in Yard Council. I am writing to discuss the recent decision the council made on the playground.",
        "Firstly, most of the youths find it difficult to use the playground because it lacks basic amenities such as the basketball court, goal posts and a sitting area for relaxation. Additionally, the maintenance policy of the playground is very poor and part of the playground has been used as a refuse dump which has brought an offensive smell to the environment.",
        "Before now, the playground used to be a great place to engage in sporting activities by the youths and other families in the neighbouring area. It is the only available space in this council that many folks utilize to engage in diverse activities, it gives room for High school students to carry out competitive sports among schools.",
        "I would suggest that the council looks into changing the management company that maintains the playground. Also, a regulatory body should be set up by the council to monitor the activities of the company and all amenities illustrated in the playground blueprint should be installed. I would be glad if my suggestions are looked into.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Simeon Agbanoma"
